@host = http://localhost:5283

### Registro de propietario
POST {{host}}/api/cuenta/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dni": 12345678,
  "nombre": "Juan",
  "apellido": "Pérez",
  "email": "juan@test.com",
  "telefono": 11223344,
  "passwordHash": "1234Juan"
}

### Login de propietario
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/cuenta/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "juan@test.com",
  "passwordHash": "1234Juan"
}

### Variable de token capturada desde el login
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

